WITH monthly_billing AS (
    SELECT
        e.event_month,
        COALESCE(p.tier, '(unknown)') AS tier,
        COALESCE(c.industry, '(unknown)') AS industry,
        COUNT(DISTINCT e.subscription_id) AS active_subscriptions,
        SUM(e.amount) AS total_mrr,
        COUNT(DISTINCT s.user_id) AS unique_users
    FROM {{ ref('int_deduped_billing') }} e
    LEFT JOIN {{ ref('stg_subscriptions') }} s
        ON s.subscription_id = e.subscription_id
    LEFT JOIN {{ ref('stg_plans') }} p
        ON s.plan_id = p.plan_id
    LEFT JOIN {{ ref('stg_users') }} u
        ON s.user_id = u.user_id
    LEFT JOIN {{ ref('stg_companies') }} c
        ON u.company_id = c.company_id
    WHERE s.status = 'active'
        AND e.event_type = 'subscription'
    GROUP BY
        e.event_month,
        COALESCE(p.tier, '(unknown)'),
        COALESCE(c.industry, '(unknown)')
)
SELECT
    event_month AS month,
    tier,
    industry,
    active_subscriptions,
    total_mrr,
    unique_users
FROM monthly_billing
ORDER BY event_month ASC
